[Manica, Matteo, Charlotte, Bunne, Roland, Mathis, Joris, Cadow, Mehmet Eren, Ahsen, Gustavo A, Stolovitzky, and María Rodríguez, Martínez. "COSIFER: a python package for the consensus inference of molecular interaction networks".Bioinformatics (2020)](https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btaa942).""" ;
