    ns1:description "Common Workflow Language example that illustrate the process of setting up a simulation system containing a protein, step by step, using the [BioExcel Building Blocks](/projects/11) library (biobb). The particular example used is the Lysozyme protein (PDB code 1AKI). This workflow returns a resulting protein structure and simulated 3D trajectories." ;
    ns1:identifier "https://doi.org/10.48546/workflowhub.workflow.29.3" ;
