    ns1:description "For integrative analysis of CAKUT multi-omics data DIABLO method of the mixOmics package (version 6.10.9. Singh et. al. 2019) was used with sPLS-DA (sparse Partial Least Squares Discriminant Analysis Discriminant Analysis) and PLS-DA classification." ;
