        <https://workflowhub.eu/workflows/354#generic_variation_analysis_reporting-outputs-all_variants_all_samples>,
        <https://workflowhub.eu/workflows/354#generic_variation_analysis_reporting-outputs-by_variant_report>,
        <https://workflowhub.eu/workflows/354#generic_variation_analysis_reporting-outputs-cleaned_header>,
