    ns1:description "Complete CUT&amp;RUN/CUT&amp;TAG analysis workflow for paired-end sequencing data. Processes raw FASTQ files through adapter removal (cutadapt) and alignment (Bowtie2 with dovetail option enabled). Applies quality filtering (MAPQ ≥ 30, concordant pairs only), converts BAM to BED format, and performs peak calling using MACS2 with parameters optimized for the punctate signal profile characteristic of CUT&amp;RUN/CUT&amp;TAG experiments." ;
