    ns1:description """Description: SSP-based RCP scenario with high radiative forcing by the end of century. Following approximately RCP8.5 global forcing pathway with SSP5 socioeconomic conditions. Concentration-driven.
Rationale: the scenario represents the high end of plausible future pathways. SSP5 is the only SSP with emissions high enough to produce the 8.5 W/m2 level of forcing in 2100.

This workflow is answering to the following scientific question:
- Is it worth investing in artificial snowmaking equipment at RATECE-PLANICA?""" ;
