    ns1:description "The workflow takes a trimmed long reads collection, and Forward/Reverse HiC reads to run Hifiasm in HiC phasing mode. It produces both Pri/Alt and Hap1/Hap2 assemblies, and runs all the QC analysis (gfastats, BUSCO, and Merqury). The default Hifiasm purge level is aggressive (l3)." ;
    ns1:image <https://workflowhub.eu/workflows/3979/diagram?version=2> ;
