    ns1:dateCreated "2025-10-01T02:01:59Z"^^ns1:Date ;
    ns1:dateModified "2025-11-27T14:15:46Z"^^ns1:Date ;
    ns1:description "Generate phased assembly based on PacBio HiFi reads and parental Illumina data for phasing. Part of the VGP workflow suite, it needs to be run after the Trio k-mer Profiling workflow VGP2. This workflow uses HiFiasm for contigging, and generates assembly statistics, BUSCO reports, Merqury plots, and the genome assembly contigs in fasta and GFA format. " ;
