    ns1:description """**Name:** Lanczos SVD  
**Contact Person**: support-compss@bsc.es  
**Access Level**: public  
**License Agreement**: Apache2  
**Platform**: COMPSs  
**Machine**: MareNostrum4  

Lanczos SVD for computing singular values needed to reach an epsilon of 1e-3 on a matrix of (150000, 150).  
The input matrix is generated synthetically.  
This application used [dislib-0.9.0](https://github.com/bsc-wdc/dislib/tree/release-0.9)
""" ;
